{"tid":2074110,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「國安法100%定罪」譚耀宗：可揀法官，中共管轄權是兜底","createTime":"2020-06-22T00:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T12:02:17.000Z","uid":52090,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd53ae76f077695fc4787ae723ff18cb1562044","tid":2074110,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:50:39.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗表示，行使管轄權，形容是一個「兜底」的做法<br />\n紅媒冇link<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定罪機會高，直接告<br />\n定罪機會中，㨂紅官再告<br />\n定罪機會零，直接送中兜底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n100%定罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再配合華為網絡監控，<br />\n下屆選舉提電子選票<br />\n有支持過五大訴求嘅200萬「極端少數份子」<br />\n就一次過捉哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得，<br />\n由2019年6月開始，<br />\n中共港共已經標籤所有和理非係<br />\n「極端少數份子」<br />\n上過街叫過五大訴求都係港獨<br />\n唔好諗住坐三年，係直接5-10年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請做好準備，香港人"},{"pid":"029323b2dd1e597020650b7c6cdb46b30b5666af","tid":2074110,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4c9f813cdb2f3ae160018ff63c5849a22e67e8a","tid":2074110,"uid":4942,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:52:44.000Z","msg":"佢捉200萬人坐即走啦<br />\n<br />\n當香港人傻嘅咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3cd9ebf2e185e54399ac6008d4a70e757db26b","tid":2074110,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:57:45.000Z","msg":"幫幫手,推上熱門"},{"pid":"ad3cd0d14fdd4f5fc214abce9777e5ce5b55c2a8","tid":2074110,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:00:39.000Z","msg":"咁等到12月了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67431fe0b52da552a8bf21ec775813c408f48914","tid":2074110,"uid":233128,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"正捉200萬人 可以去外國申請難民資格去移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacb355a3d9d1a780175d12bbace9bd48fc757bd","